{"mode":2,"id":"S001","scripts":[{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#fff157","say":"ねえノーフォークちゃん、鉄血の戦艦がここを通るって聞いたよ！あの子にちょっかい仕掛けたら、女王様からもきっと褒めてもらえるって！","actor":900004,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"さ、最新鋭戦艦なんて、ノーフォークたちは勝てるのですか…？","actor":900005,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"それにここは冷たくて、ノーフォークもう凍りそうですぅ…早く任務を終わらせて母港に戻りましょう…？","actor":900005,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":1},{"expression":"4","nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"say":"大丈夫！私たちはあくまで偵察で、戦闘になったら姉貴たちがいるよ！それにみんなが結構すぐ近くにいるから、いざとなっても援護してくれるからね～","actor":900004,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":0},{"expression":"5","nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"say":"それにここまでは何もなかったし、新鋭艦はもしかしたらもう逃げちゃったかもしれないよ~","actor":900004,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"本当にいたらどうしよう……早く母港に帰りたいです…あれ？","actor":900005,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"えっと…この前の海域に異常があるようです","actor":900005,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":1},{"expression":"9","nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"なになに？見せて見せて","actor":900004,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":2},"side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"これは…鉄血の駆逐艦隊！偵察部隊かもしれないけど、フッド姉に連絡して！","actor":900004,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"あ、あの…実は発信機のアンテナ、凍りついていたのです…","actor":900005,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":2},"side":1},{"expression":"10","nameColor":"#a9f548","painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"say":"……とりあえず偵察部隊を足止めするね！小規模の量産型相手ならきっと大丈夫！","actor":900004,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"side":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"や、やっぱり戦闘ですか？…うぅ…悪い予感がしてたのに…","actor":900005,"painting":{"time":0.5,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":2},"side":1}]}